  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\nPush notification is not shown if user who sends a notification is not added to contacts by a receiver\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nPush notification is shown on top of the screen\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nPush notification is not received\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status on 2 devices\r\n- Create new account on both devices\r\n- USER_1: add user_2 to contacts via: Scan QR code, or entering public key\r\n- USER_2:  run app on background \r\n- USER_1 send message to user_2\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: any\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS",
